        <briefdescription>
<para>Perform a system power off. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function will perform an immediate power off of the system. It is the responsibility of the caller to ensure that the system is in a safe state to be powered off. Any required wake up sources must be enabled before calling this function.</para>
<para><computeroutput>CONFIG_POWEROFF</computeroutput> needs to be enabled to use this API. </para>
